---
// src/components/About.astro
---
<section class="py-24 md:py-32 px-6 relative overflow-hidden" id="about">
    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-1/3 h-full bg-primary/5 -z-10 skew-x-6 transform origin-top-right"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12 lg:gap-20">
            
            <div class="flex-1 order-2 lg:order-1">
                <div class="relative group max-w-md mx-auto lg:max-w-none">
                    <div class="aspect-square rounded-[3rem] lg:rounded-[4rem] overflow-hidden shadow-2xl relative z-20">
                        <img alt="Baker sprinkling sugar on cake" class="w-full h-full object-cover hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700" src="https://images.ctfassets.net/gcwac57vok7r/4pwYejZXZLbAlSqJLy7J1/3ed13effbdb0e317b91c6dce161c9750/GettyImages-942403044__1_.jpg?w=680&h=511&q=90&fit=fill&fm=jpg" />
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex-1 order-1 lg:order-2 text-center lg:text-left">
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <span class="text-primary font-display font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-4 block">Our Origin</span>
                    <h2 class="text-5xl md:text-8xl font-display font-black leading-[0.9] mb-8 md:mb-12 text-slate-900 dark:text-white">
                        What is <br /> Panchasara?
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-6 text-xl md:text-2xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 leading-relaxed font-light">
                        <p>
                            Derived from the Malayalam word for <span class="text-primary font-bold">Sugar</span>, 
                            Panchasara is the "sweet spot" where tradition meets modern commerce.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We believe every home <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">studio</span> has a story worth telling. Our mission is to provide the digital infrastructure so you can focus on your craft, while we handle the pixels.
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white pt-4">
                            Built for creators, by people who love handmade.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
        </div>
    </div>
</section>